All this libraries you can install them manually by tipical linux commands such as: 

 - ./configure
 - make 
 - make install

All installed libraries will be installed by default at usr/local/bin, and shared libraries at 
usr/local/lib. Important: For shared libraries you need to refhes them with this command: 

 - "sudo /sbin/ldconfig"

After all in orther to exec the right mtdev2tuio script you can use this or similar line command: 

- "sudo ./mtdev2tuio /dev/input/event13 osc.udp://127.0.0.1:3333"

Note: "mtdev2tuio" is an script in "mtdev2tuio-master" folder

